Subject: Server OS Update
Description: We conduct Tenable scans on the EPP server, which provide a significant number of critical and high findings. We deployed our instance from a AWS AMI provided by CoSoSys. Is there a newer AWS AMI for the EPP server based on a more recent Ubuntu version? Is there documentation regarding migrating from one EC2 instance to another?
Solution_Comment__c: We migrated the EPP server with System backup V2 and we also resized the partitions.
